title: Faber-Castell Young Artist Texture Painting Kit
description:
This set has everything your budding artist will need to experiment with color, texture, paint, and patterns.  Kit contains 5 assorted texture brushes, 5 colors of washable 10 fl oz tempera paints, 1 paint mixing bowl, 20 sheets  of paper, and a reusable storage bag.

Illustrated instructions and ideas are also included.
